name: Cryptobourrin
tagline: A small set of hand made cryptographic tools
body:
This repo is where I put some of the code I write.
Quality is low 
Usability is uncertain
Support is weak

-- To build :
gcc -o wiener wiener.c -lgmp 
gcc -o weger  weger.c -lgmp -lm
